Hesitant
/Ancient-Aetherium/placeholder.png
Reward: 2
Your character is prone to wait a second before jumping into battle with their party. They typically act last, making them draw initiative twice, and taking the worse of the two cards.

Oblivious
/Ancient-Aetherium/placeholder.png
Reward: 3
Your character knows how to act, but not how to react. Unable to notice their situation and act accordingly, those with Oblivious will be unable to use Unbound Actions. Instead, any Unbound Action becomes part of their Turn.
